{"tid":1090022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=？保安趕返工遭小巴撞飛命危","createTime":"2019-04-03T07:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T07:39:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a08c586732df33c56a115180e8c66d952ef7b00e","tid":1090022,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"葵涌發生交通意外。今早(3日)7時53分，一輛由浩景臺開往荃灣的91號專線小巴，姓鄭(65歲)司機沿麗瑤街落斜，當駛至麗瑤邨樂瑤樓對開時，撞倒一名過路姓蔡(64歲)男子，事主頭及手腳受重傷昏迷，由救護車送院搶救後，情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n警方在場調查意外原因，小巴左車頭損毀，稍後由拖車拖走扣驗。經調查後，小巴司機涉嫌危險駕駛導致他人身體嚴重傷害被捕。傷者的兒子趕抵醫院了解，獲悉父親傷勢後，情緒激動蹲在地上，傷者經搶救後，送到深切治療部病房留醫。據了解，事主居住麗瑤邨，<span style=\"color: red;\">任職保安員，當時他正趕往上班。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/bkn-20190403090544422-0403_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190403%2Fbkn-20190403090544422-0403_00822_001.html&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5JUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=ec9a6bca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/bkn-20190403090544422-0403_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9901e42234514f29f179ac94af6d874c219c4d31","tid":1090022,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/photo/bkn-20190403090544422-0403_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190403144659\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190403090544422-0403_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190403144659&h=3ed94fb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a2241e564a6e895ce9ac898b8e83cab24f20854","tid":1090022,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}